    "date": "2020-05-21T13:50:06Z",
    "text": "Protect American Nationals During Emergencies by Mitigating the Immigration Crisis Act or the PANDEMIC Act\n\nThis bill requires the removal from the United States of any unlawfully present alien in U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement custody during a national emergency related to a communicable disease. This requirement does not apply to an alien facing charges for a crime of violence."
